Class BioSQLFeatureFilter.ByNoteTermOnly

  • java.lang.Object

    public static final class BioSQLFeatureFilter.ByNoteTermOnly
extends BioSQLFeatureFilter.HibernateFeatureFilter
    A filter that returns all features that have a note with the given term. The value and rank is not checked.
